lass=\"faq_answer\" id=\"ans-2\">Applying to Ready Set Funds will not affect your credit score. We and our lending partners request what\'s called a \'soft pull\' on your credit score, which does not affect your score.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<hr class=\"faq\">\r\n			<div class=\"faq_wrapper\">\r\n				<h3 class=\"faq_question\" id=\"q-3\" onclick=\"toggle_ans(3)\">Can I apply if I have a low or poor credit score?</h3>\r\n				<p class=\"faq_answer\" id=\"ans-3\">Absolutely. Focused offers programs from bankable clients to borrowers that are new-to-credit, or are non-prime due to any reason. Our lending partners take holistic approaches to underwriting and some do not review credit reports at all.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<hr class=\"faq\">\r\n			<div class=\"faq_wrapper\">\r\n				<h3 class=\"faq_question\" id=\"q-4\" onclick=\"toggle_ans(4)\">Do you work with startup businesses?</h3>\r\n				<p class=\"faq_answer\" id=\"ans-4\">Yes, startups are limited to equipment financing and our cash-out program. Once you have been in business for 3 months, we can provide additional financing programs for the business.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"bio_modals\" class=\"modals\">\r\n	<div id=\"patrick\" class=\"bio_wrapper\">\r\n		<div class=\"bio\">\r\n			<img src=\"https://www.pinclipart.com/picdir/big/209-2098523_individuals-person-icon-circle-png-clipart.png\" width=\"20%\" height=\"auto\" class=\"float_left\">\r\n			<div class=\"bio_title\">\r\n				<h2>Patrick Harman</h2>\r\n				<hr>\r\n				<span class=\"x\" onclick=\"toggleBio(\'patrick\');\"></span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<p>Patrick partnered with ReadySetFunds in 2019 to bring continued success in helping today\'s small business owners achieve their financial growth. Patrick most recently worked for a small debt fund in Manhattan where he discovered a niche in the industry, “rather than take advantage [of business owners], let’s educate and truly help in an honorable manner”. With over 5 p