2\" onclick=\"toggle_ans(2)\">Will applying affect my credit?</h3>\r\n				<p class=\"faq_answer\" id=\"ans-2\">Applying to Ready Set Funds will not affect your credit score. We and our lending partners request what\'s called a \'soft pull\' on your credit score, which does not affect your score.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<hr class=\"faq\">\r\n			<div class=\"faq_wrapper\">\r\n				<h3 class=\"faq_question\" id=\"q-3\" onclick=\"toggle_ans(3)\">Can I apply if I have a low or poor credit score?</h3>\r\n				<p class=\"faq_answer\" id=\"ans-3\">Absolutely. Focused offers programs from bankable clients to borrowers that are new-to-credit, or are non-prime due to any reason. Our lending partners take holistic approaches to underwriting and some do not review credit reports at all.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<hr class=\"faq\">\r\n			<div class=\"faq_wrapper\">\r\n				<h3 class=\"faq_question\" id=\"q-4\" onclick=\"toggle_ans(4)\">Do you work with startup businesses?</h3>\r\n				<p class=\"faq_answer\" id=\"ans-4\">Yes, startups are limited to equipment financing and our cash-out program. Once you have been in business for 3 months, we can provide additional financing programs for the business.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"bio_modals\" class=\"modals\" onclick=\"biosOff();\">\r\n	<div id=\"patrick\" class=\"bio_wrapper\">\r\n		<div class=\"bio\">\r\n			<img src=\"https://www.pinclipart.com/picdir/big/209-2098523_individuals-person-icon-circle-png-clipart.png\" width=\"20%\" height=\"auto\" class=\"bio_img\">\r\n			<div class=\"bio_title\">\r\n				<h2>Patrick Harmon</h2>\r\n                                <div class=\"text-biz_title\">Managing Partner</div>\r\n				<hr>\r\n				<span class=\"x\" onclick=\"biosOff();\"></span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<p>Patrick partnered with ReadySetFunds in 2019 to bring continued success in helping today\'s small business owners achieve their financial growth. Patrick most recently worked for a small debt fund in Manhattan where he discovered a niche in the industry, “rather than take advantage [of business owners], let’s educate and truly help in an honorable manner”. With over 5 plus years of experience in small business lending, he has helped over thousands of business owners attain what all small businesses need- infusions of capital to promote healthy growth. There is one phrase that comes to his mind when working with business owners: The Capital You Need For The Business You Deserve. When he’s not helping business owners you can find him outdoors whether it be snowboarding in the winter, or sneaking in a quick 9 holes.</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"peter\" class=\"bio_wrapper\">\r\n		<div class=\"bio\">\r\n			<img src=\"https://www.pinclipart.com/picdir/big/209-2098523_individuals-person-icon-circle-png-clipart.png\" width=\"20%\" height=\"auto\" class=\"bio_img\">\r\n			<div class=\"bio_title\">\r\n				<h2>Peter Francis</h2>\r\n                                <div class=\"text-biz_title\">Managing Partner</div>\r\n				<hr>\r\n				<span class=\"x\" onclick=\"biosOff();\"></span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<p>Peter Francis serves as a Managing Partner at ReadySetFunds.  His primary expertise lies in his experience as a relationship manager and strategic partnerships liaison.  He brings a wealth of knowledge in mezzanine financing as well as helping to introduce clients across a spectrum of business sectors to the world of structured finance. Prior to ReadySetFunds, Peter served as Director of Sales for Qualify My Business, a small business financial firm situated in the alternative finance sector.  His experience at Qualify My Business afforded him the opportunity to provide his clients the value that his strong network of alternative financial partnerships bestows.  It was during this time that Peter recognized the absence of appropriate strategic planning and support that so many businesses are in want of.  At ReadySetFunds, Peter endeavors to fill this void by i